Subject: RE: [T2] Main Harness - how difficult to replace


If you have to take out the dash and are really getting into this project I
guess you may as well bite the bullet and replace the harness. I would try
and do it piece by piece. Only disconnect what you are ready to reconnect.
Kind of like doing plug wires on a V12 Jag... Take a lot of pictures before
you start so you will have some reference, and get really friendly with
your Bentley wiring schemes. Good Luck

